<h1 id="task-5-mini-ctf">[Task 5] Mini CTF</h1>

<blockquote>
  <p>Thereâ€™s a web server running on <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">http://MACHINE_IP:8081</code>. Connect to it and get the flags!</p>
</blockquote>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><!-- <td class="rouge-gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
